commit.message:
added more difficulty

the game's difficulty now increases significantly as players gain more eggs. very difficult lmao

basic background

added a basic background to the game. image can be changed by editing the source for the Rectangle in the .kv file

added score/life corner anchoring

score and life counters are now placed based on the width of the window, instead of based on an absolute coordinate (which can cause scores to become blocked when resizing window)
